or misfits.

654
00:32:35.914 --> 00:32:38.083
Hudson:
We became close friends.

655
00:32:38.124 --> 00:32:39.584
We are close friends today.

656
00:32:39.626 --> 00:32:42.045
and I think she is
one of the best people.

657
00:32:42.712 --> 00:32:45.382
Griffin: That kind
of loving bond between them.

658
00:32:45.423 --> 00:32:47.217
the soulmate connection.
if you will.

659
00:32:47.258 --> 00:32:50.595
becomes all the more important
later in life.

660
00:32:51.554 --> 00:32:55.558
Anders: George Stevens
had complicated characters

661
00:32:55.600 --> 00:33:00.146
and he cared about
those characters
within society

662
00:33:00.230 --> 00:33:02.982
in a way that's different
from how Sirk did.

663
00:33:03.900 --> 00:33:05.694
Now look here. Sarge.

664
00:33:05.777 --> 00:33:09.239
I'd sure appreciate it
if you were a little more
polite to these people.

665
00:33:09.280 --> 00:33:11.199
Oh. you would. would you?

666
00:33:11.282 --> 00:33:12.951
Anders:
By the end of that movie.

667
00:33:13.034 --> 00:33:15.036
Rock Hudson
is our American hero

668
00:33:15.120 --> 00:33:19.290
because he's inclusive
