01:08:35.823 --> 01:08:37.742
That's you. sir.
It's CB talk.

1398
01:08:37.826 --> 01:08:41.287
Kevoian:
And he didn't cast me
from a casting couch.

1399
01:08:41.371 --> 01:08:43.915
There was only one time
that he ever.

1400
01:08:43.997 --> 01:08:47.585
um. asked me to possibly
be intimate.

1401
01:08:47.627 --> 01:08:52.006
And I. I chose.
um. the different path.

1402
01:08:52.090 --> 01:08:53.966
(chuckles)

1403
01:08:54.050 --> 01:08:57.429
I was 23 and a lot cuter.

1404
01:08:58.971 --> 01:09:01.265
He was fun
and then he was elegant.

1405
01:09:01.349 --> 01:09:07.063
and. you know. I only saw him
pee in the bushes once.

1406
01:09:07.104 --> 01:09:09.441
(chuckling)

1407
01:09:11.151 --> 01:09:14.738
Hey! What's going on here?

