01:23:22.961 --> 01:23:25.422
Even we thought it was AIDS.

1712
01:23:25.714 --> 01:23:27.674
All right.
how did you know?

1713
01:23:27.757 --> 01:23:29.592
I saw his hand.

1714
01:23:30.218 --> 01:23:32.887
-What did you see?
-The beginning of a lesion.

1715
01:23:32.971 --> 01:23:34.472
Discoloration.
