1926
01:33:15.720 --> 01:33:18.723
And I was told. uh.

1927
01:33:18.765 --> 01:33:23.687
"Rock is not capable
of knowing who you are

1928
01:33:23.728 --> 01:33:27.232
"and you are better
remembering him

1929
01:33:27.273 --> 01:33:29.234
in a better time."

